Stoneship site
==============

This is the source for the Stoneship site (<http://stoneship.org/>), which
is my personal web site. This site is provided as an example to show off
how nanoc can be used.

Requirements
------------

You will need nanoc 3.1 or higher, as well as `builder`, `BlueCloth`,
`RubyPants` and `Hpricot`.

